{
  "texts": [
    "For very new topics like the one on which I tested them above, they have difficulty determining which references are the most useful-a critical skill for human researchers who work at the frontier.",
    "Moreover, I found it highly useful to provide significantly more context for Deep Research queries than in regular chatbot interactions.",
    "Even though they perform research for anything from a few minutes to half an hour, the exact amount of reseach that they engage in is sometimes difficult to steer-in part because model providers need to limit their costs.",
    "For example, a query like \"Perform task X for each of the 50 States of the US\" is technically feasible, but for complex tasks X, it quickly reaches the internal limits that model providers have set for the use of typical Deep Research systems.The table below lists several of the top providers of Deep Research systems, their availability, and how they differ in their features.",
    "As can also be seen from the chat examples above, Gemini Deep Research proposes a research strategy after receiving the user's prompt, asking for confirmation of the path that it intends to pursue."
  ]
}